Description: Icons paths fixed to match freedesktop guidelines
 Original desktop file and icons location prevented icon theming without
 editing the launcher file. This patch moves icons under
 /usr/share/icons/hicolor/XXxXX/apps and removes specific file name
 and file extension from launcher file.
Author: vir@ctm.ru
Origin: <upstream|backport|vendor|other>, <URL, required except if Author is present>
Bug: https://github.com/vir/yate/issues/7
---
